      "title": "Sustainability Dashboard",
      "type": "text",
      "options": {
        "mode": "markdown",
        "content": "## Carbon Awareness\n\nThis dashboard will display carbon intensity, energy usage, and emissions data once the Carbon Engine (Task 8) is implemented.\n\n**Planned panels:**\n- Current grid carbon intensity (gCO2/kWh)\n- Energy usage over time (Wh)\n- Cumulative emissions (gCO2)\n- Carbon-aware scheduling status\n- Deployment emissions per build"
      }
    },
    {
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus" },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": { "unit": "percent" },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "gridPos": { "h": 8, "w": 12, "x": 0, "y": 4 },
      "id": 2,
      "title": "System Power Proxy — CPU Usage",
      "description": "CPU usage as a proxy for power consumption until real power monitoring is available",
      "type": "timeseries",
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "100 - (avg(rate(node_cpu_seconds_total{mode=\"idle\"}[5m])) * 100)",
          "legendFormat": "CPU %"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus" },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": { "unit": "bytes" },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "gridPos": { "h": 8, "w": 12, "x": 12, "y": 4 },
      "id": 3,
      "title": "Network I/O (proxy for activity)",
      "type": "timeseries",
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "rate(node_network_receive_bytes_total{device!=\"lo\"}[5m])",
          "legendFormat": "RX {{ device }}"
        },
        {
          "expr": "rate(node_network_transmit_bytes_total{device!=\"lo\"}[5m])",
          "legendFormat": "TX {{ device }}"
        }
      ]
    }
  ],
